#description HearthKeep Room Monitor - nRF52833 + BGT60TR13C
#
# Room monitor schematic for HearthKeep elder safety system.
# Components:
# - nRF52833 (BLE 5.0, Cortex-M4, 512KB Flash)
# - BGT60TR13C (60GHz FMCW mmWave radar, 1Tx/3Rx)
# - BME688 (temperature, humidity, pressure, VOC/IAQ)
# - TSL25911 (ambient light sensor)
# - SX1261 (868MHz LoRa radio)
# - AP2112-3.3V regulator
# - USB-C + 3× AA battery backup
# - RGB LED, setup button
# - IP65 enclosure option for bathroom
#
# This is a placeholder - full KiCad schematic to be created.
#End